* Remove Obsolete\nData with VACUUM
** What it does
***_ Removes unreferenced data files
***_ Files older than retention threshold
***_ Permanently deletes data
** Syntax
***_ VACUUM <table>
***_ VACUUM <table> RETAIN N HOURS
** Impact
***_ Time travel to removed versions fails
***_ Irreversible operation
** Deletion vectors
***_ Mark rows as deleted without rewrite
***_ VACUUM alone doesn't purge them
***_ Requires REORG TABLE ... APPLY (PURGE)
@endmindmap
